My advice:  be willing and able to direct the tanks. If the assistant tanks, nukers, ect...do not use /assist maintank, let them know how dangerous it may be for them and everyone involved. If everyone takes out the hardest mob of the bunch, the fight goes much faster, with a better success rate, and without having to heal three or four people instead of just the tank and yourself<br>
